com.mattrader.common

Class MessageCom

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mattrader.common.MessageCom

  • class MessageCom
extends java.lang.Object
    This class help transforming String messages received by Directa Darwin into a data structure easier to parse. A MessageCom essentially is a HashMap in which information are stored in key-value pairs
